# Harry Eubank King

Harry Eubank King (1902â€“1981) was a lawyer and state legislator in Florida. He served in the Florida Senate from 1941 to 1956. He was a Democrat. The Florida Archives have photographs of him. He represented Polk County, the 7th District.
He served as City Attorney for Winter Haven.
